    "subtitle": "How do you actually work with others? Five collaboration species and where you fit in a team.",
    "description": "<p>This maps what you genuinely do when work involves other people — not a wish-list of ideals. Mark your first and second instinct in each scenario. If several feel true, pick the one that most often wins when the pressure is real.</p><p>Invite three or more people to compare and see your team constellation.</p>",
    "duration": "10 scenarios. Approximately four minutes.",
    "privacyNote": "Your answers stay in this browser. The result belongs to you. Sharing is your choice.",
    "disclaimer": "Original instrument. This is not a validated psychometric assessment.",
    "startButton": "Map my species"
  },
